item.title: CVE-2018-6331|2024-08-05T06:01:48.362Z -- facebook -- buck
item.description: Buck parser-cache command loads/saves state using Java serialized object. If the state information is maliciously crafted, deserializing it could lead to code execution. This issue affects Buck versions prior to v2018.06.25.01.
